# krakentag-privacy
We're Using Your Microphone so that you can Talk to Oher People in Realtime.
Usage Data is collected automatically when using the Service.

IP Address:
your IP address is saved in your Playfab/krakentag account, and is only used for for IP bans in-game or to give specific players acces to Moderation Stuff

Other services we use:
We can't control what the other services we use do. If you want to read more on these services, go to these links:
 
 Photon - https://dashboard.photonengine.com/en/Account/PrivacyAndCookiePolicy
 Playfab - https://playfab.com/terms/
 
 You may contact us about deleting your data and removing your playfab account from our server.
 
 You Can Contact us Under this E-Mail: 
 
